instructions.text:
• In a small bowl, combine cucumber, vinegar, a pinch of sugar (we used ¼ tsp;
½ tsp for 4 servings), salt, and pepper. Cover with plastic wrap and microwave
until sugar dissolves, 15-30 seconds. Stir and set aside to pickle.

